         </unitdatestructured>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_3061b76632b0829eb5f2b55e46ad84d0">
            <language>The materials are in Bosnian, Croatian, and Serbian.</language>
         </langmaterial>
         <abstract id="aspace_96663a2b337ed725cfb9ee39047e9e92">The collection comprises campaign brochures, flyers, and posters representing the various political parties that participated in the 2006 October 1st general election to determine the presidency and parliament seats of Bosnia and Herzegovina; entity parliaments for the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, as well as the Republika Srpska; and canton parliaments.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <arrangement id="aspace_4ee6105aa59a984a5d9017ede87b77d0">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged alphabetically by name of political party.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_b22e3105c785c228acd8cf8ee4a18657">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection comprises campaign brochures, flyers, and posters representing the various political parties that participated in the 2006 October 1st general election to determine the presidency and parliament seats of Bosnia and Herzegovina; entity parliaments for the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, as well as the Republika Srpska; and canton parliaments.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <custodhist id="aspace_28fd6ac307a318a32b73706eb5403249">
         <head>Custodial History</head>
         <p>The collection was transferred from the Slavic and East European curator, 2008.</p>  
      </custodhist>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_498fcd345de77d888821245ff8ed1daf">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_bbb278f641e09bc88a2b5d422376c950">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
